Our Human Genetics Programme has an excellent opportunity for an Advanced Research Assistant to join our interdisciplinary highly collaborative team of academics, clinicians and drug discovery researchers for a 3 year fixed term contract.This is an exciting opportunity to apply single cell genomics to cells isolated from patients with inflammatory bowel disease (IBD) or healthy control patients.
